                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; headings and incipits of the texts;
                           directives for the ministers; most of the abbreviations; elements of the
                           punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.
 
 The text in fol. 5r
                           and the incipits of most Anaphoras are written alternately in red and
                           black lines (s. fols. 82v, 87v, etc.).</seg>
                     </handNote>
